race.comment: VIN SANTO (5) kept on the fresh side after ploughing through the heavy (8) going for a dominant maiden win over 1400m at Kembla Grange on September 13. Kept up to the mark with a 1030m trial at Rosehill. Has options from the draw and Latham retains the ride. Goes close. SOCIABLE (2) has impressed in both runs back and a win looks imminent. Went forward from the low draw when a gritty third over 1000m at Kembla Grange with the 59kg. Will roll forward from the gate and the tight track suits. KOIOS (3) encouraging return from a long break when he shouldered the 59kg for a closing second over 1250m at Newcastle. Comes out of a strong contest and can go on with the job on his home track. RIDE THE RIVER (4) marginally better effort at his second run back when a plugging sixth over 1000m at Kembla Grange. Will need luck from the draw and place claims look best.
